'''Heinz Strobl''' ([[4 December|December 4]], [[1952]]), also known as Gandalf, is an Austrian composer and producer. He released an album titled [[Visions 2001]] in [[2000]] which was filled with [[J.R.R. Tolkien]]-related songs.
